The paper deals with optimization of linear precoding and decoding in a multiuser MIMO system, which involves information theory, networking, signal processing, machine learning, and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SI (Signal Processing), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
